official_title: Concurrent resolution expressing the sense of the Congress that the embargo of Cuba not be lifted as long as Cuba is under Communist control.

summary.text: Expresses the sense of the Congress that the embargo of Cuba not be lifted and that relations not be normalized as long as Cuba is under Communist control, or object to the American presence in Guantanamo, or fails to compensate Americans for property seized by the Castro regime.

titles.title: Concurrent resolution expressing the sense of the Congress that the embargo of Cuba not be lifted as long as Cuba is under Communist control.
